### Get User Communities Summary
### Returns aggregated dashboard data for the authenticated user's communities
### Includes: community stats, pending requests, pool distributions, and invites

@baseUrl = http://localhost:3000/api/v1
@token = {{$dotenv KEYCLOAK_TEST_TOKEN}}

### Get Communities Summary
# GET /api/v1/user/communities/summary
# Returns:
# - communities: Array of user's communities with member counts, trust scores, pending request counts
# - pendingActions.incomingRequests: Requests TO user's wealth (pending)
# - pendingActions.acceptedOutgoing: User's requests that were accepted (awaiting fulfillment)
# - pendingActions.poolDistributions: Pool distribution requests for user (pending/accepted)
# - invites: Pending community invites for user

GET {{baseUrl}}/user/communities/summary
Authorization: Bearer {{token}}
Content-Type: application/json

